name: The lake side
description: Step by step on the edge of the lake while the sun went down in a park larger than the central park in new york, in the background you could see a temple where the 3 popes who have visited Colombia have given their sermon, the planes circled over it sky while they waited to be authorized to land, through some speakers the warning was heard that the park was going to close and it was urgent that we leave it, not yet please! I need to finish taking some more photos until the end of the day!
